description.p:
said direction determining means are formed of an assembly including an antenna and a GPS type receiver for determining the geographical coordinates of the location in which said timepiece is situated;


the 6 o'clock-12 o'clock axis of said timepiece is used as a reference axis; and


at least said first hand is arranged so as to be able to indicate the direction of the "target" location with respect to said reference axis.

